        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Protecting Our Widows and Widowers in Retirement (POWR) Act</b></p> <p>This bill increases Old Age, Survivors, and Disability Insurance benefits for widows or widowers in two-income households by establishing an alternative benefit based on combined household benefits.</p>]]></text>
